descriptor.name: Cosmetics
descriptor.short_desc:
The Glossier Invisible Shield Water-Gel Transparent Face Sunscreen SPF 351

Invisible protection: This lightweight, water-gel sunscreen absorbs quickly into the skin without leaving a white cast or greasy residue. It's perfect for everyday wear under makeup.

Broad spectrum SPF 35: Protects against UVA and UVB rays to help prevent sunburn, premature aging, and skin cancer.

Hydrating formula: Contains hyaluronic acid to help keep skin hydrated and plump.

Oil-free and non-comedogenic: Won't clog pores or cause breakouts.

Suitable for all skin types: Gentle enough for even sensitive skin.

descriptor.short_desc:
Eye-catching and unique: This bright yellow rotary phone is sure to add a pop of color and personality to any home or office. It's a great conversation starter and a surefire way to make a statement.

Classic design: The rotary dial and traditional handset evoke a sense of nostalgia, while the sleek, modern design keeps it feeling fresh and up-to-date.

Functional and fun: This phone is not just a decorative piece; it's a fully functional landline phone that can be used to make and receive calls. It also has some great features, like caller ID and redial.

High quality: This phone is made from durable materials and is built to last. It's also easy to set up and use.

descriptor.short_desc: This retro yellow rotary telephone is the perfect addition to any home or office. It's not only stylish, but it's also functional, with a clear and crisp sound quality. The rotary dial is easy to use, and the phone comes with a cord that's long enough to reach even the most remote corners of your room.

descriptor.name: Dove Cream
descriptor.long_desc:
The product in the image is a Dove Nourishing Body Care Rich Nourishment Cream. It is a white, opaque cream that comes in a blue and white plastic tub. The tub has a white flip-top lid. The front of the tub has the Dove logo, the words "Dove Nourishing Body Care," and the words "Rich Nourishment 24hr Intensive Moisturisation."

The Dove Nourishing Body Care Rich Nourishment Cream is a deeply moisturizing cream that is suitable for all skin types. It is made with a blend of nourishing ingredients, including shea butter, coconut oil, and glycerin. The cream is designed to provide long-lasting hydration and to leave your skin feeling soft, smooth, and healthy.

Here are some of the key features of the Dove Nourishing Body Care Rich Nourishment Cream:

Provides 24 hours of intensive moisturization
Nourishes and hydrates the skin
Leaves skin feeling soft, smooth, and healthy
Suitable for all skin types
Dermatologist-tested and allergy-tested
